These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, goat, rat
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, radish, plum
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
3 different games are played: monopoly, domino, snooker
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person eating radish and the person eating plum##2
4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Pet         | goat | horse   | rat   |
| Food   | radish     | strawberry | plum |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | cola    | hot-chocolate      |
| Game     | domino     | monopoly      | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, april, october
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, iced-tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, action
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold, aconite
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person watching action movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person who growssunflower is between the person drinking tea and the person who's birthday is in october##2
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Birthday          | april  | may     | october     |
| Beverage   | tea     | iced-tea     | hot-chocolate      |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | disaster | comedy |
| Flower           | aconite | sunflower     | marigold       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
City: marseilles, liverpool, berlin
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, canadian
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, ivory
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, surfing, water-polo
1. the argentine is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the canadian and the person who likes ivory##2
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| City          | marseilles  | berlin     | liverpool     |
| Nationality           | canadian | argentine  | chinese   |
| Color   | yellow  | blood-red    | ivory |
| Sport           | water-polo     | skateboarding | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
House: cape-cod, colonial, tower
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, tiparillo
3 different games are played: monopoly, go, whist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, june
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the colonial house is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the tower house is between the game-smoker and the person playing monopoly##2
4. the colonial house is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| House    | cape-cod       | tower  | colonial   |
| Cigar     | game    | tiparillo  | bluemaster |
| Game     | go   | whist | monopoly        |
| Birthday   | june | november     | december      |

