3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, canasta
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, police-officer, musician
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, australian, brazilian
1. the musician is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the malaysian is between the musician and the person playing canasta##2
3. the person playing chess is the australian##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the malaysian is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Transport          | snowmobile    | motorbike     | quad-bike      |
| Game         | chess | backgammon | canasta |
| Job   | musician  | police-officer       | project-manager       |
| Nationality           | australian     | malaysian       | brazilian     |

