3. the person playing poker is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the baccarat-smoker##2
4. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
