2. the fan reggae is between the videographer and the owner of the turtle##2
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
5. the fan reggae is between the fan ambient and the person playing canasta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Job          | videographer      | project-manager   | social-worker |
| Music-Genre         | electronic | reggae | ambient |
| Game   | canasta      | billiard | monopoly   |
