3. the security-guard is in the middle##1
4. the security-guard is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to london##2
5. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
