3. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the fan indie is on the left of the fan gospel##1
5. the fan indie is between the owner of the dog and the person driving the van##2
6. the person driving the tram is the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Music-Genre      | disco | indie      | gospel            |
| Pet           | snake | ferret | dog |
| Transport   | van     | trike        | tram         |
| Food   | lettuce  | plum    | cabbage        |

