The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, skydiving, reading
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, jet-ski
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, rock
1. the person who likes lilac is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is reading##2
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the fan rock##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan r&b##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Color      | chestnut    | lilac          | light-blue |
| Hobby          | reading | skydiving           | dancing        |
| Transport           | motorbike | jet-ski | skateboard         |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | rock    | r&b      |

