.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, cain, havana
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, collecting
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, weightlifting
3 different games are played: billiard, bridge, go
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person playing billiard##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
6. the havana-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar           | cain   | havana   | old-henry |
| Hobby   | collecting | dancing   | cooking     |
| Sport   | rowing     | biathlon      | weightlifting    |
| Game           | billiard | bridge | go    |

