.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, baseball, lacrosse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, november, january
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, nurse, doctor
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, subway
1. the person driving the airplane is the doctor##1
2. the nurse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the coach is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's birthday is in october##2
4. the nurse is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person who's sport is baseball and the nurse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | snowboarding | lacrosse     | baseball        |
| Birthday         | november   | january | october |
| Job   | nurse        | coach       | doctor      |
| Transport           | subway           | snowmobile    | airplane       |

