.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy, lily
House: cottage, townhouse, victorian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, vegafina, aristoff
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, azure, amber
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the townhouse house is the person who likes orange##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes orange##1
4. the havana-smoker is the person who growslily##1
5. the victorian house is between the person who likes amber and the vegafina-smoker##2
6. the aristoff-smoker is the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Flower        | daisy      | azalea | lily |
| House         | townhouse     | victorian    | cottage        |
| Cigar       | vegafina | aristoff   | havana   |
| Color   | orange          | azure     | amber       |

 